high_descs: Turn to the left and move forward. Turn left to face the short side of the counter.
Pick up the ladle from the edge of the counter.
Carry the ladle and turn to the left, then right and move to the counter.
Place the ladle in the pan, toward the back of the counter.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Carry the pan and turn around, then right. Turn right and then face the white table on the left.
Place the pan on the left front side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a ladle and pan to the table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a scoop on the counter.
Turn and go to the counter.
Put the scoop in the pan on the counter.
Pick up the pan on the counter.
Turn and go to the round table in the corner.
Put the pan on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a scoop to the round table.

high_descs: Take one step forward and turn left and walk to the white door, turn left and face the counter.
Pick up large gold spoon with a black handle.
Turn left for four steps, turn right and walk over to the counter.
Place the spoon in the pan, standing up with the handle up.
Pick up the pan with the spoon still in it.
Turn around and walk five steps, turn right walk to the end of the counter and turn right for six steps, turn left to face the table.
Set the pan on the table next to the bread loaf on the left side, with the handle of the pan facing the middle of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan, with a spoon in it, on the table.
